    "h1": { "en": "Frame", "zh": "框架" },
    "lede": { "en": "Aluminum extrusions, T-nuts, brackets, and bumpers form the mechanical chassis everything else bolts onto. Squareness built in here governs every motion downstream.", "zh": "铝型材、T 型螺母、角码和缓冲脚共同构成机械底盘，其余部件都装在它上面。这里打好的方正度，决定了之后所有运动的精度。" }
  },
