      {
        "h3": { "en": "Drop-in, not slide-in", "zh": "落入式，而非滑入式" },
        "body": { "en": "One joining plate reinforces each corner. Its drop-in T-nuts seat into the closed frame and quarter-turn to lock, so you never have to take the frame apart.", "zh": "每个角用一块连接板加固。它的落入式 T 型螺母直接落进已封闭的框架，转四分之一圈即锁紧，全程无需拆开框架。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:100mm; width:80mm;"
      }
    ],
