    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Feet point down", "zh": "脚朝下" },
        "body": { "en": "The four bumpers are the machine's feet, mounted under the frame. Each screw runs up from below — through the bumper and into a drop-in T-nut in the bottom slot — so the heads tuck out of sight underneath.", "zh": "四个缓冲脚就是机器的支脚，装在框架底下。每颗螺钉自下往上穿过缓冲脚，旋入底部型材槽里的落入式 T 型螺母，钉头便藏在底面之下。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:100mm; width:78mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Use the screws that come with the bumpers", "zh": "使用缓冲脚自带的螺钉" },
        "body": { "en": "Many bumpers ship with their own screws. If yours do, fit those — they're sized to match the bumper.", "zh": "很多缓冲脚出厂就自带螺钉。如果你的带螺钉，就用自带的，尺寸正好与缓冲脚配套。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:135mm; top:30mm; width:70mm;"
      }
    ],
    "bom": {
